            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指開報23960，跌88點或0.37%，低水75點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">科指期貨開報 5308，跌33點或0.62%，低水23點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">國指期貨開報8690，跌43點或0.49%，低水40點。</p>\n</div>",
